org.energy_home.jemma.javagal.layers.object
Class WrapperWSNNode

java.lang.Object
  org.energy_home.jemma.javagal.layers.object.WrapperWSNNode

public class WrapperWSNNode
extends java.lang.Object

Class used to encapsulate any ZigBee Node. This class manage the Timers for the Algorithms Discovery, Freshness and ForcePing

Author:
"Ing. Marco Nieddu or from Consoft Sistemi S.P.A., financed by EIT ICT Labs activity SecSES - Secure Energy Systems (activity id 13030)"
